Welcome to our Crumbl summer fair week! Join Brelynn and Gabe from Crumbl HQ unbox this week's pink box, sharing their favorites, and kicking off this week's Crumbl Fair Game. 🎡💕
 
In addition to bringing fair flavored cookies, we will be hosting our own Crumbl Fair Game! Listen closely in this episode for your FIRST hint in our fair game, then stay tuned as we share a new hint each day on one of our social media platforms! 

The platform will switch daily so make sure you are paying close attention, to gather all the clues. Keep an eye out on Friday for where you should submit your final answer! The first FIVE people to put together the clues win a swag bag! Who's ready to CRUMBL?! 😉🍪

Back to school has never been so SWEET! 🍎✏️🍪  August 23 - 28: 👇  🥛 CHOCOLATE FT. OREO®
A chocolate cookie featuring OREO® topped with rich vanilla cream cheese frosting and dusted with OREO® crumbs. 
🥜 PEANUT BUTTER JAMWICH
A chilled peanut butter cookie sandwich filled with peanut butter mousse and raspberry jam. 
🍫 CHOCOLATE MALLOW CUPCAKE (NEW)
A warm chocolatey cookie stuffed with a creamy vanilla mallow filling, topped with a chocolate glaze and dressed with swirls of white chocolate 
🧸 GRAHAM CRACKER FT. TEDDY GRAHAM®
A crumbly graham cracker cookie topped with a pillow of sweet honey butter frosting and finished with a light drizzle of honey and Teddy Graham® crackers. 
🍉 WATERMELON
A pink vanilla sugar cookie topped with a perfect swirl of watermelon frosting and topped off with a watermelon gummy.

🍪 MILK CHOCOLATE CHIP
A warm cookie with milk chocolate chips.  🚨 GIVEAWAY CLOSED🚨 Like & tag three friends on this post 👇 for a chance to win a FREE party box! We will announce the winner tomorrow on our story.  #TasteWeekly #CrumblCookies #PinkBox  📲 www.crumbl.com/app

Are you ready for ANOTHER week!?  August 16-21: 👇

🥜 BUCKEYE BROWNIE A chocolate brownie cookie with a peanut butter buckeye layer and covered with melted semi sweet chocolate. 
🍯 HONEY BUN (NEW)
A warm soft cinnamon cookie, swirled and brushed with a honey butter glaze.

🎉 CONFETTI CAKE
A confetti sugar cookie topped with a fluffy swirl of pink vanilla cream cheese frosting and finished with large confetti sprinkles.   🍊 ORANGE CREAMSICLE (NEW) A chilled tangy orange cookie, studded with white chips and packed with a creamy vanilla cheesecake filling.
 🍭 CLASSIC SUGAR Our classic sugar cookie base topped with a perfect pink swirl of almond-flavored frosting.  🍪 MILK CHOCOLATE An award-winning warm cookie with milk chocolate chips.

🚨 GIVEAWAY 🚨
Like & tag three friends on this post 👇 for a chance to win a FREE party box! We will announce the winner tomorrow on our story.

#TasteWeekly #CrumblCookies #PinkBox

📲 www.crumbl.com/app
